When would you want to use a remote repository rather than keeping all your work local?

When your work with other or you are working on multiply devices, or you want public your repositary

Why might you want to always pull changes manually rather than having Git automatically stay up-to-date with your remote repository?

Every time when you update branch you must merge changes. Automatically merges can be harmful and manual merge to often.

Describe the differences between forks, clones, and branches. When would you use one instead of another?

Fork use want clone project on GitHub
Clone - when you don't want change original.
Branch -when you possible merge with original.